      "date": "2020-04-22 23:58:49.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review-1\n\n(27 comments)\n\nThis definitely needs to have some test cases to verify that it is working.  Up until this point, it was hard to know if the code could be tested, but here it should be possible to run sanity-flr.sh or similar with an EC file layout to verify that EC resync and EC read rebuild is working.\n\nIt might be possible to test this code earlier in the series (e.g. patch https://review.whamcloud.com/38064 \"LU-12668 ec: resync parity component\" by writing a synthetic data pattern to the file, and then using \"lfs mirror read\" to dump the parity component and verifying in userspace that the parity was computed correctly.",
